            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>First look at the new playable character in action.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Cygames [285 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/cyberagent/cygames">Cygames</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Cygames Osaka [34 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/cyberagent/cygames/cygames-osaka">Cygames Osaka</a> have released the first “Meet the Crew” trailer for <em><a title="Games > Granblue Fantasy: Relink - Endless Ragnarok [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/granblue-fantasy-relink-endless-ragnarok">Granblue Fantasy: Relink – Endless Ragnarok</a></em>, introducing new playable character Beatrix (voiced by Jennifer Losi in English, Aya Hirano in Japanese).</p><p><em>Granblue Fantasy: Relink – Endless Ragnarok</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3839790/Granblue_Fantasy_Relink__Endless_Ragnarok_Upgrade_Kit_Standard_Edition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on July 9. A closed beta test will run from March 13 to 16.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Meet the Crew: Beatrix</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="[EN]Granblue Fantasy: Relink - Endless Ragnarok | Meet the Crew: Beatrix" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1hOWx1eihRc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
